Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,True Calendar, year 71.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,JIOR, a proponent of peace through neutrality, had enjoyed economic prosperity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.09,0:00:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but came under sudden, overwhelming attack by the Dorssia Military Pact Federation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The JIOR government quickly conceded to their demand of unconditional surrender,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,but Haruto Tokishima, a student in the developing colony of Module 77,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,climbed aboard the Valvrave, a mysterious weapon, and drove off the Dorssian forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorssia and ARUS are now in a contest to determine who will control the Valvrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result of the declaration by Shoko Sashinami, the daughter of JIOR's president,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.58,0:00:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,their school has become an independent country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.88,0:00:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...want to be famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These things are cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Will she make the perfect guinea pig?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,ARUS' pilots all died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,People all around the world will hear my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Saki Rukino? Sure, I know her! 'La-la-lalalala,' right?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.12,0:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it'll make me special, I'll do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, she... Is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's all be free...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm a vampire! That makes me a bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You had no idea what would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you give up your humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about all the people you care about whose hearts you're going to break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're indestructible, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have anyone that I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Poverty, abuse, alcoholism, crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.45,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, my parents were like poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way I had to escape from them, from that lousy world, was to become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.79,0:03:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any family or friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.33,0:03:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything I can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, a friend is crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a genuinely nice guy, aren't you, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.50,0:04:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,...that was all a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I look forward to working with you, Miss Nanami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, you're the representative of the newborn JIOR.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on... I can't be a representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its a teacher's job to lead her pupils, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll see you on the moon, then.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher? I'm just a trainee...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... the one that's one level further down...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, we—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I check these numerical values to tweak the output of the transmitter system, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a gift for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make a fine technician.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying that you have talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She skipped her turn on the cleaning chores rota again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because she's a celebrity, she thinks she—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.00,0:06:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so wound up all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:06:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you girls safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, and your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,There's too many words coming out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tokishima?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I plugged it up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll expect to see you cheering me on in the next battle, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's fun to be a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl was compatible with the system?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidden weapons, the school curriculum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The conclusion I'm led to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...is that this school itself is a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why am I being taken off the mission?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Cain's orders are absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Lord" Cain, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, which rank is higher, a captain or a prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relaying Captain Cain's exact words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say you can't obey, then—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man of Karlstein, the chosen elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware of the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Haruto. I gotta say, I never took you for a bad boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we see more, you love guru you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Watari was crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's against the rules to make a move on an idol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a gentlemen's agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea, taking my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today, I'd like to introduce you to my little sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, I call her that, but she's not my real little sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's someone who means as much to me as a real little sister, though.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm marketing myself as the surrogate little sister of a celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said that you wanted to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A promise is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I paid you in advance, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Haruto, what was it like to be a lonely vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, I had always—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! Really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who isn't you is posting under your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's all that easy to fool the wired's retinal authentication system.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this isn't Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Her songs are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And out of all of us, she worked the hardest on the music video the other day."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto would never say that one person worked harder than someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. A girl I made friends with recently knows all about this kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have her look into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it when Haruto is friendly with other girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are friendly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.69,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no big deal! It's not like we kissed or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.11,0:10:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kissed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no! I didn't say kissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, um... Dissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but it sounded perverted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.08,0:10:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And you had a perverted look on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.12,0:10:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I don't care about Haruto at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're already a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you already plenty famous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. Why would you do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if you don't leave your mark on the world, you'll just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a rough intro...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.18,0:11:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.31,0:11:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That sound's an emergency broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We decided on it earlier, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone, please listen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're under Dorssian attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.15,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat, we're under Dorssian attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.28,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're under Dorssian attack!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean they followed us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we go to the control room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.82,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please take shelter immediately!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:36.87,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I really mean it! Dorssian forces are here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But why? What about Shoko's threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That we'd hand over the robot to ARUS?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The declaration should have reached Dorssia, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the ARUS ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to contact them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We're completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But how? When did they—?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Lagrange 4 forces have secured the area ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have them surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they just couldn't catch up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping for a chance to catch them in a pincer movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They kept us waiting too long for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go! C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If we gave ARUS the robot, wouldn't Dorssia surround them and give us time to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.28,0:12:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But they'd be—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's ARUS doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Call Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's "VVV IV"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.42,0:12:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.42,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to call Tokishima!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino's piloting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been found out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, where did you get that robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.14,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her name's Carmilla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.93,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Calling it "robot" or "Valvrave" doesn't fit my image.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From now on, call my Valvrave "Carmilla," okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm launching. See ya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.15,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's lots of those robots...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.70,0:12:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave up on expecting anything from others a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.87,0:13:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do this myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What weapons do I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Spindle Knuckles... These, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said there was more than one of those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Carmilla, you're the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, you're going out too far ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.28,0:14:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? We're indestructible superhumans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two Valvraves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Its loadout seems somewhat different, but we'll proceed according to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys seem pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my analysis, the Valvrave is a close-quarters combat weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,In short, if it can't get close, its combat effectiveness is cut in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whittle it down bit by bit, and victory is assured!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're up against Ideals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no easy matter to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, then! That's the battleship sorted out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.93,0:15:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No... Senator Figaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,ARUS was...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get away! Right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.40,0:15:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.03,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave... There's a pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pair?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruto! I have to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I shaking like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I'm immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The green one is just sitting there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Trade places with me, you chicken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.08,0:16:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, are you oka...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch where you're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Takahi-senpai, why are you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This? Um, I... was asked to cheer them on, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get anywhere near them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do your harakiri thing this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.12,0:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The instant you stop, I'm gonna grab you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pull yourself together, Saki Rukino!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can save Haruto and us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sashinami, you can't just—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The eyes of the entire school are on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to act that pathetic when everyone's watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're putting on a show!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki Rukino is a star, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A star...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This audience is way too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm gonna be the biggest star in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stream this battle to the wired.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.90,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The feed from my cockpit, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's that robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fighting again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't I know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's that former idol. From JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl who retired?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me! I just had an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.97,0:18:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many they send out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming famous is the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She's no match for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.22,0:19:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But she's doing—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, they have her on the defensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.35,Alt,,0,0,0,,We don't know that yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They took out that ARUS ship in the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you saying should pilot it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.15,0:19:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Saki Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.66,Alt,,0,0,0,,Shoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Saki Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sashinami, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheering her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself earlier, remember, senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rukino, fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.37,0:19:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing in sports!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.35,0:20:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a cheering section gives players a huge boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.46,0:20:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hardly the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bunch of nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's all it took to win, we'd—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it together, Saki Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.93,0:20:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You join in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.56,0:20:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let em beat ya, Saki Rukino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.27,0:20:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, go for it... go for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Saki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.82,Alt,,0,0,0,,- Don't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:28.82,Alt,,0,0,0,,- Fighting women are so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's like a dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.82,0:20:30.65,Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't get shown up by that boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world... is watching.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.04,0:20:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You hurt me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mocked me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How can it be so manoeuvrable?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The world that tried to kill me is now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(642.094,474.5)}NOTICE OF CONTRACT TERMINATION
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...by the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's closed the gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,X-eins!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.59,0:21:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait! Retreat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an5\pos(636.981,628.5)}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.56,0:21:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All forces, retreat to L2!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat, all forces, retreat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.14,0:21:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this an order, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring X-eins' escape pod into hangar #2.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all right with this, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another plan in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,L-elf...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sake of our friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.97,0:22:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.72,0:24:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, episode 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.78,0:24:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,"Haruto Under the Rubble".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will expose the truth of the world.
